The Mobilome Antimicrobial Resistance Taxonomy Extraction Script (MARTES) is a pipeline that include the mobilome and taxonomical analysis for those ARG-carrying contigs obtained in metagonomic analysis, with some improvements of the pipeline employed in [Quijada et al., 2025](https://doi.org/10.1038/s41564-025-02059-8), including the use of:
[Platon](https://github.com/oschwengers/platon) ([Schwengers et al., 2020](https://doi.org/10.1099/mgen.0.000398)), [PlasmidFinder](https://github.com/genomicepidemiology/plasmidfinder) ([Carattoli et al., 2014](https://doi.org/10.1128/aac.02412-14)) and [Genomad](https://github.com/apcamargo/genomad) ([Camargo et al., 2024](https://doi.org/10.1038/s41587-023-01953-y)) for plasmid detection
[integron finder](https://github.com/gem-pasteur/Integron_Finder) ([Néron et al., 2022](https://doi.org/10.3390/microorganisms10040700)) to detect integrons
[MobilomeElementFinder](https://bitbucket.org/mhkj/mge_finder/src/master/) ([Johansson et al., 2021](https://doi.org/10.1093/jac/dkaa390)) for other mobile genetic elements, including of miniature inverted repeats (MITEs), insertion sequences (ISs), transposons (Tns), composite transposons (ComTns), integrative conjugative elements (ICEs), integrative mobilizable elements (IMEs) and cis-mobilizable elements
[Kraken2](https://github.com/DerrickWood/kraken2) ([Wood et al., 2019](https://doi.org/10.1186/s13059-019-1891-0)) for taxonomic assignment of ARG-carrying contigs, with the use of [Conifer](https://github.com/Ivarz/Conifer) to improve Kraken2 annotation.
an in-house ruby script ([AMR_merge_info_v3.rb]()) developed by José F. Cobo-Díaz and Elena Fernández-Trapote to merge all the obtained information

Furthermore, several R-scripts for high-quality figure plots are available to work from the matrix generated by AMR_merge_info_v3.rb.
